{"tid":452003,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點樣分辨自己有無抑鬱症","createTime":"2017-10-29T18:10:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-01T02:38:24.000Z","uid":45678,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8c4ef896d9679eb573d42bb91d72f33412ba50ce","tid":452003,"uid":45678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T18:10:50.000Z","msg":"如題 抑鬱有乜症狀? <br />\n<br />\n講下自己狀況先: 失眠咗成個禮拜 考慮緊好唔好食安眠藥 有時會有尋死嘅念頭(雖然唔忍心令愛我嘅屋企人傷心) 覺得每日存在都係行屍走肉 無乜目的 喺任何社交圈子都不被重視 <br />\n<br />\n求教 謝謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b352741bccff8595f402e44e3061508ba5429c22","tid":452003,"uid":2917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T18:11:39.000Z","msg":"我都想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3418e8760c53d97a654eff867eb0492bd49ee03d","tid":452003,"uid":87750,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T18:13:41.000Z","msg":"抑鬱係唔會覺得不被重視 <br />\n反而會因為不被重視而鬆一口氣"},{"pid":"a2f646ef5863dcbd769594a2d3e722061a0d47f3","tid":452003,"uid":48577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T18:13:45.000Z","msg":"有唔識點分辨 但有咩唔開心記住講出來 唔好屈係心入面"},{"pid":"b11190e17470bb2da89bf99046b605492c474069","tid":452003,"uid":105665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T18:14:03.000Z","msg":"同樓主情況差唔多<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"c070fe8a620f91dec0d155f321f447131c3b3ae6","tid":452003,"uid":45678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T18:21:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同樓主情況差唔多<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我係因為後悔同ex分手 然後有日喺街撞到ex同新男朋友一齊 就受咗好大刺激"},{"pid":"acde1d4fa5e849e2966724f167981c840f6b40